4501 /// Some comparisons can be simplified.
4502 /// In this case, we are looking for comparisons that look like
4503 /// a check for a lossy truncation.
4504 /// Folds:
4505 ///   icmp SrcPred (x & Mask), x    to    icmp DstPred x, Mask
